First Department,

January, 1970

(January 6, 1970) State Commission for Human Rights, on the Complaint of New York Urban League and Another, Appellant, v. Edmund M. Speer, Jr., as Trustee Under the Will of Edmund M. Speer, Deceased, et al., Respondents.

Application pursuant to section 298 of the Human Rights Law [Executive Law] transferred to the Appellate Division, Second Department, for review and determination, pursuant to CPLR 5711. Concur — McGivern, J. P., Markewieh, Nunez, McNally and Tilzer, JJ.
